36:27.853 --> 36:29.753
- Yeah, what,

36:29.755 --> 36:31.421
what are you doing?

36:31.423 --> 36:32.856
I just, uh,

36:32.858 --> 36:34.558
you know, I was wondering
if you remember

36:34.560 --> 36:36.526
<i> what game it was</i>

36:36.528 --> 36:39.829
we pulled that
prank on Boiter?

36:40.265 --> 36:42.599
'Cause I gotta-I gotta-I
gotta group of people here

36:42.601 --> 36:44.834
and they were, uh...

36:44.836 --> 36:46.836
they-they were
wondering and I said,

36:46.838 --> 36:48.972
I know who has the memory
of a fucking elephant.

36:51.192 --> 36:53.409
