37:04.523 --> 37:06.406
- Uh, I don't know, Terry.

37:06.407 --> 37:08.290
Why don't you call him at
two in the morning and ask him?

37:09.828 --> 37:12.262
- Okay.

37:13.332 --> 37:15.498
Okay. Okay.

37:21.707 --> 37:23.974
I'm going.

37:32.951 --> 37:36.453
Ah! Ahhh!

